WEBVTT

00:04.422 --> 00:06.750
Hank, if your neck is
so sore all the time,

00:06.780 --> 00:09.280
why don't you just buy a new mattress?

00:09.320 --> 00:10.630
Who am I, Warren Buffet?

00:10.660 --> 00:11.980
I'm on a fixed income.

00:11.990 --> 00:15.720
I can't just be buying a new
mattress every 25 years.

00:15.723 --> 00:18.380
Yeah, I get all my
mattresses from the street.

00:18.400 --> 00:21.370
Sometimes they even come
with a free raccoon.

00:21.390 --> 00:23.640
All right, Hank, I'm just
gonna very gently...

00:23.660 --> 00:24.809
Okay, now... Whoa!

00:24.810 --> 00:26.640
Oh! You demon!

00:26.680 --> 00:29.689
Wait a minute. Wow. You fixed it.

00:29.690 --> 00:31.080
- Oh.
- Nice work, demon.

00:31.090 --> 00:32.180
Mm.

00:32.759 --> 00:33.980
Well, Sid.

00:34.000 --> 00:35.630
- Ah.
- I'm off to Milan

00:35.660 --> 00:37.279
for a week... again.

00:37.280 --> 00:40.940
Listen, I have some rather fickle ficus.

00:41.000 --> 00:44.260
You sure you can handle watering
my plants while I'm gone?

00:44.340 --> 00:46.960
I know you poors don't like to work.

00:46.980 --> 00:48.760
You know it.

00:48.790 --> 00:51.091
Everybody, this is Edie.

00:51.092 --> 00:54.129
She lives over in Shady Meadows West,

00:54.130 --> 00:56.360
where the rich people live.

00:56.390 --> 00:58.259
I wandered over there once,

00:58.260 --> 01:01.420
and Edie was kind enough
to escort me out.

01:01.440 --> 01:03.040
Here's the key.

01:03.060 --> 01:06.059
Be sure to remove your shoes on the rug.

01:06.060 --> 01:09.600
And I must insist you
sit when you urinate.

01:09.620 --> 01:12.300
Ooh, do we stand when we do number two?

01:12.330 --> 01:15.489
Oh, forget I said that.

01:15.490 --> 01:17.760
Uh, uh, don't you worry.

01:17.770 --> 01:21.900
I'm going to treat your fickle
fici as if they were my own.

01:21.940 --> 01:23.780
See that you do.

01:23.950 --> 01:25.680
Toodily oodily.

01:27.680 --> 01:29.630
Gee, I hope they let
her through security

01:29.640 --> 01:31.660
with that stick up her butt.

01:31.690 --> 01:34.900
Sid, why would you do anything
for that snobby woman?

01:35.900 --> 01:38.930
Any other stupid questions, stupid?

01:41.640 --> 01:43.469
Sorry.

01:43.470 --> 01:46.480
Living the high life is getting to me.

01:47.980 --> 01:50.060
Oh, it's plastic.

01:52.000 --> 01:58.074
Learn the unknown English words
of this movie at www.skeebdo.com

