16:49.040 --> 16:50.650
That is sugar, Hank.

16:50.680 --> 16:54.360
So... now you gonna get ants.

16:54.420 --> 16:57.540
And-and how you gonna
sell all these cookies

16:57.580 --> 16:59.659
if you can't find them?

17:01.280 --> 17:03.280
Oh, I'll save the cookies for...

17:03.300 --> 17:06.020
Ah! Hot, hot, hot, hot tray!

17:07.359 --> 17:08.368
- Oops.
- Oh!

17:08.369 --> 17:09.868
Sorry. My bad.

17:09.869 --> 17:12.628
Oh, you are such a baby!

17:12.630 --> 17:15.459
Would a baby ever do this?

17:18.920 --> 17:22.260
Hey! Look at yourselves.

17:22.300 --> 17:24.219
This was supposed to be fun,

17:24.220 --> 17:26.259
and now you're tearing
at each other's throats.

17:26.260 --> 17:28.889
And for what?

17:28.890 --> 17:32.649
A little extra money?

17:32.650 --> 17:34.979
- You can't enjoy cookies...
- Oh!

17:34.980 --> 17:36.479
