17:36.480 --> 17:37.729
Stop it!

17:37.730 --> 17:39.219
Stop it!

17:39.220 --> 17:41.819
What the hell is the matter with you?!

17:41.820 --> 17:45.300
I told you how important this
was to me, and you ruined it!

17:45.330 --> 17:47.300
Why?! Why, Hank?

17:47.320 --> 17:49.409
Because I did something you couldn't do?

17:49.410 --> 17:52.460
- What's that, have babies?
- There's that, too!

17:57.780 --> 18:01.720
Can somebody show me how
to turn this thing off?

18:11.320 --> 18:14.180
Boy, she's working
that ball pretty hard.

18:14.200 --> 18:16.859
Should we wait till she
tires out a little?

18:16.860 --> 18:18.779
No, let's get right to it.

18:18.780 --> 18:20.939
Charlie, you go in first.
You've seen combat.

18:20.940 --> 18:23.609
Uh, you don't survive by going in first.

18:23.610 --> 18:25.320
All right.

18:26.120 --> 18:28.949
Hey, girl. How's your day going?

18:28.950 --> 18:31.039
Go away. I'm busy.

18:31.040 --> 18:32.959
Uh, listen,

18:32.960 --> 18:36.200
I'm not very good at
apologies, so, um...

18:36.240 --> 18:38.040
we cool?

18:38.060 --> 18:40.940
What Hank means to say

18:40.960 --> 18:43.660
is that he's sorry. That's
what you mean to say,

18:43.680 --> 18:45.739
Hank, right? I don't want
to put words in your mouth,

18:45.740 --> 18:48.759
but you tell Margaret
you're sorry right now.

18:48.760 --> 18:51.720
I'll say I'm sorry when I'm ready.

18:52.390 --> 18:54.979
All right, I'm ready.

18:54.980 --> 18:58.190
So, um, I'm not good with apologies,

18:58.220 --> 18:59.750
but I was watching that show, uh,

18:59.760 --> 19:00.899
- This Is Us.
