19:00.900 --> 19:04.609
And the black dude on the
show would say, uh...

19:04.610 --> 19:08.419
I can kind of be a jerk when
people tell me what to do.

19:08.420 --> 19:10.409
Especially when they're right.

19:10.410 --> 19:12.619
Well, I-I'm kind of the same way.

19:12.620 --> 19:13.939
Except I'm usually right,

19:13.940 --> 19:16.789
so it's not that big
of a problem for me.

19:16.790 --> 19:18.560
Hey, Tom, don't be petty.

19:20.280 --> 19:21.640
No?

19:22.420 --> 19:25.049
Look, guys...

19:25.050 --> 19:27.000
when I watched my ex-husband

19:27.020 --> 19:28.429
run our business into the ground,

19:28.430 --> 19:31.889
I swore I would never let
a man steamroll me again.

19:31.890 --> 19:35.229
I mean, I love hanging out
with you guys, but I'm...

19:35.230 --> 19:37.059
sick of being condescended to.

19:37.060 --> 19:38.859
I'm sick of being ignored,

19:38.860 --> 19:40.299
- I'm sick of being...
- Margaret...

19:40.300 --> 19:43.240
I'm sick of being interrupted.

19:44.300 --> 19:47.199
It's not the 1950s, you guys.

19:47.200 --> 19:50.240
Times have changed, and
you have to change, too.

19:50.300 --> 19:52.419
I'm not saying you have to
agree with me all the time,

19:52.420 --> 19:54.370
