19:54.420 --> 19:56.579
Well, Margaret, you know what they say.

19:56.580 --> 19:59.499
Men are from Mars, and women are from...

19:59.500 --> 20:01.980
Well, my mother was from Philadelphia,

20:02.000 --> 20:04.000
- but she grew up in a small...
