20:04.780 --> 20:07.929
We were stupid to not listen to you.

20:07.930 --> 20:11.600
Yeah, and if your ex didn't
listen to you, he's stupid, too.

20:12.980 --> 20:14.540
You know, if we all pitch in,

20:14.550 --> 20:17.480
